---

# {{ run_id }} {{ brief_type | replace("-", " ") | title }} — {{ phase }}

*Generated {{ moment().format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm') }} · Agent: `{{ agent_author }}`*
*Blueprint: [[Brief-Assembly.blueprint]] · Schema: [[VAULT-SCHEMA]]*

---

{% section "Session Briefs (Auto-Assembled)" %}
<!-- Dataview pulls all brief atoms for this run/session -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Brief",
  brief_type AS "Type",
  phase AS "Phase",
  agent_author AS "Agent",
  hypothesis_touched AS "Hypotheses",
  review_status AS "Status"
FROM "00-SHARED/Session-Briefs"
WHERE type = "brief"
  AND (run_id = this.run_id OR session_id = this.session_id)
SORT ts ASC
```
{% endsection %}

{% section "Hypothesis Movement" %}
<!-- Confidence changes across all briefs in this session -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Brief",
  confidence_delta AS "Delta",
  hypothesis_touched AS "Hypotheses",
  evidence_tier_touched AS "Tiers"
FROM "00-SHARED/Session-Briefs"
WHERE type = "brief"
  AND (run_id = this.run_id OR session_id = this.session_id)
  AND length(hypothesis_touched) > 0
SORT ts ASC
```
{% endsection %}

{% section "Blockers" %}
<!-- Blockers flagged across session briefs -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Brief",
  blockers AS "Blockers",
  agent_author AS "Agent"
FROM "00-SHARED/Session-Briefs"
WHERE type = "brief"
  AND (run_id = this.run_id OR session_id = this.session_id)
  AND length(blockers) > 0
SORT ts ASC
```
{% endsection %}

{% section "COC Linkage" %}
<!-- Forensic chain-of-custody references -->

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| COC Session File | `{{ coc_session_file }}` |
| Agent Version | `{{ agent_version }}` |
| Git Commit | `{{ git_commit }}` |
| Atom File | `{{ atom_file }}` |

*Full forensic detail: see session COC .jsonl file (local, not in vault).*
{% endsection %}

{% section "Related Briefs (Siblings)" %}
<!-- Other briefs from same sprint/investigation -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Brief",
  brief_type AS "Type",
  phase AS "Phase",
  created AS "Date"
FROM "00-SHARED/Session-Briefs"
WHERE type = "brief"
  AND investigation_id = this.investigation_id
  AND sprint_id = this.sprint_id
  AND file.name != this.file.name
SORT ts DESC
LIMIT 10
```
{% endsection %}

